column2: ggplot(data, aes(x = serum_creatinine)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.2, colour =  "white", fill = "plum", alpha = 0.7) + labs(title = "Histogram of Creatinine in Blood") + geom_density(eval(bquote(aes(y=..count..*0.2))),colour="black") + geom_vline(xintercept = 0.59, linetype = "dashed") + geom_vline(xintercept = 1.35, linetype = "dashed")
